        <div class="col-sm-9 view-section-details">
          <p>Tired of going to multiple websites to get the best price for a product? Worry no more! Get the best price for a product from a single interface 
          in ProductGrabber.</p>

          <p>Track the price of a product across different online shopping websites and get notified when the price of a product changes. No more visiting multiple 
          websites multiple times a day just to get the best price!</p>
          
          You can check out the project on <a href="https://github.com/scalableinternetservices/ProductGrabber">GitHub</a> or view the project page on <a href="https://www.pivotaltracker.com/n/projects/1446080">Pivotal</a>.
