        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-9 view-section-details">
          <div class="input-group">
            <p>
            <ol>
              <li>The user searches for a product of interest across different online shopping portals using the ProductGrabber interface.</li>
              <li>The user then selects the required products which have to be tracked.</li>
              <li>ProductGrabber will constantly monitor the price of the product selected by the user.</li>
              <li>ProductGrabber will notify the user if there is a change in the price of a product he/she is tracking.</li>
              <li>The user can then go to the online shopping portal from the ProductGrabber interface and purchase the product.</li>
            </ol>
          </p>
